<p><b>WINTER SHELTER</b>. We are in urgent need for
volunteers who can stay overnight on Sundays or
Mondays. On those evenings, we welcome homeless
men 50 years old and over. Please also consider
supporting the Winter Shelter by donating spray cans
of men’s deodorant as well as pillowcases.
